# Merlin ToDo

## Orb speaking settings voice command

- Add a deterministic local command flow before the AI model for orb speaking settings.
- Support setting and querying live orb speaking deformation settings by voice.
- Required settings:
  - speaking deformation strength
  - speaking pose speed
- Example commands:
  - "please set speaksettings for the orb to 1"
  - "set orb speaking speed to 1.2"
  - "set orb speaking deform strength to 0.8"
  - "what is current speaking speed for the orb?"
  - "what is the current orb speaking deform strength?"
  - "reset orb speaking settings"
- Save values to a live settings file and load them on reboot.
- Bypass the AI model when the command is handled locally.
- Return a short confirmation/query response through the existing UI/speech response path.
